# P4CE — iOS CrossFit Training App

## What this project is
An iOS-first training tracker for CrossFit and hybrid athletes. The primary value is an adaptive programming engine, not pretty UI. Users are mid-workout and exhausted — every interaction must be instant.

## Tech stack
- SwiftUI + SwiftData (no backend, offline-first)
- Swift Charts for analytics
- MVVM architecture
- XCTest + Swift Testing
- Swift 6.0, iOS 17+ deployment target
- XcodeGen (`project.yml`) — regenerate with `xcodegen generate` after adding files/targets

## Primary simulator
iPhone 17 Pro (logical 402 × 874 pt)

```bash
cd p4ce/p4ce && xcodegen generate && xcodebuild \
  -scheme P4CE \
  -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone 17 Pro' \
  -configuration Debug build
```

